(Britton) Gagnon &amp; G. P. Lewis var. 
<emphasis id="B926EAF8E934C731FCABC8AA37D8FC22" bold="true" box="[863,977,911,938]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="293">myabense</emphasis>
